name: PR QI Status
query:
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT p.name as "Reference:Link/Purchase Receipt:300",
    p.modified as "Modified:Date:100"
    from `tabPurchase Receipt` p WHERE p.name = ALL (SELECT reference_name FROM `tabQuality Inspection` WHERE docstatus = 1) AND p.docstatus = 0
UNION
SELECT p.name as "Reference:Link/Stock Entry:300",
    p.modified as "Modified:Date:100"
    from `tabStock Entry` p WHERE p.name = ALL (SELECT reference_name FROM `tabQuality Inspection` WHERE docstatus = 1) AND p.docstatus = 0
) prj
ORDER BY 2 DESC
